name: Local Biz Web Solutions
overview:
People use search engines every day to find businesses such as yours, and if they can’t find you because your Website ranks poorly, your money could be better spent here for advertising, it works. The further back your page landing number is, the less chance you stand of being chosen, because the customer chose somebody else who ranks higher in searches.

Let us get your Website on page one where you will be noticed.

If your business doesn’t have a Website, we can host, design, optimize, and maintain your Website for you. No technical skills at all are required, we handle it all for you, as opposed to other “walk you through the process” companies. We spare you of all the hassle and confusion.
